item.content:encoded:
Any day, every day. This cropped long-sleeve top is there with sleek, stretchy fabric to support you. Thumbholes and a classic elastic bottom band help keep the top in place so you can feel comfortable and covered with every movement. Sweat-wicking tech helps you keep your cool even as you turn up the heat on your workout.

 

Benefits

  • The jacquard bottom band sits snugly against your skin without pinching or binding.
  • Nike Dri-FIT technology moves sweat away from your skin for quicker evaporation, helping you stay dry and comfortable.
  • Thumbholes let you extend your coverage and help hold the sleeves in place while you move.

 

Product details

  • 83% polyester/17% elastane
  • Machine wash
  • Imported
  • Colour Shown: Baroque Brown/White
  • Style: FV5484-237
  • Country/Region of Origin: Vietnam

item.description:

  • Colour Shown: Earth/Black
  • Style: FN2587-227

item.content:encoded:
Day or night, rain or shine, Nike Running Division offers the features you need to navigate the concrete, cars and crossings of the paved landscape. With advanced engineering and sweat-wicking tech, this snug mid layer is ready to help you stay dry and cool no matter what your day has in store.

 

Benefits

  • Nike Dri-FIT ADV technology combines moisture-wicking fabric with advanced engineering and features to help you stay dry and comfortable.
  • Thumbholes let you extend your coverage and help hold the sleeves in place while you move.
  • A curved hem allows you to easily move through your full range of motion.
  • A 1/2-zip design makes changing easy.

 

Product details

  • 47% nylon/47% polyester/6% elastane
  • Machine wash
  • Imported
  • Not intended for use as personal protective equipment (PPE)
  • Colour Shown: Earth/Black
  • Style: FN2587-227
  • Country/Region of Origin: Sri Lanka
